Nemesis Enforcer/Koga Shuko/Anubis/Hades/Unitron/Scattershot/Oblitertron:

Oblitertron stumbled back slightly from the laser blasts from Radistor, 
throwing their sword  at Radistor's sternum.  Kicking their right foot to the 
side, the large foot went towards the People's Base like a wrecking ball.  
Pulling out a plasma rifle from subspace, Dark One in control of the gestalt, 
it took aim quickly, firing off a few plasma blasts at Radistor's abdomen 
(region stomach is in).
---------------
Koga Shuko laughed, smiling even more as he saw the Truths attacking the 
base, raising his missile launcher, he fired a missile at Plintissa (if she 
is visible to them, if she's in the base, the misslie goes at the base).
--------------
Unitron raised his missile launcher, firing a rocket off at Radistor's left 
knee, firing three optic lasers at Dracona (if she is visible, if not, at the 
People's base).
------------
Anubis fired a rocket off at Radistor's left shoulder.
------------
Hades fired a rocket off at the middle of Radistor's pelvis.
-----------
Scattershot looked at the gestalts, and decided not to get involved, tossing 
down to charges at the People's base.

(Just to let the people participating in this fight know, I'll be gone for 
about an hour or so eating at a resaurant after this, so... also TheCode, if 
you do wrestling moves, you'll have to define them, I won't know what they 
are)
